376
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:45,520
I'll be back before midnight.

377
00:24:48,120 --> 00:24:49,160
Then...

378
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:50,120
Next Saturday...

379
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:51,680
Can I go with you?

380
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:52,440
No.

381
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:56,960
