391
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,440
Pull yourself together!

392
00:25:58,840 --> 00:25:59,880
Pull yourself together!

393
00:26:00,080 --> 00:26:00,800
Kuea!

394
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:03,640
You can't be like this.

395
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:06,920
Don't forget why you're here.

396
00:26:36,350 --> 00:26:37,130
Hello.

397
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,180
What's the matter?

398
00:26:38,470 --> 00:26:39,210
Kuea!

399
00:26:39,230 --> 00:26:40,220
Where are you?

400
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:41,380
I'm at Hia's house.

401
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:44,640
