402
00:26:44,650 --> 00:26:45,740
Hia Lian?

403
00:26:47,190 --> 00:26:48,220
Jong-Kook!

404
00:26:48,410 --> 00:26:49,720
The Korean producer!

405
00:26:50,050 --> 00:26:50,970
What?

406
00:26:51,510 --> 00:26:52,960
How is that possible?!

407
00:26:53,830 --> 00:26:55,130
