424
00:28:35,550 --> 00:28:37,250
What's wrong?

425
00:28:38,050 --> 00:28:39,330
A personal issue?

426
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:54,590
I won't tell you.

427
00:28:55,670 --> 00:28:56,910
I'm not like Kon-Diao.

428
00:28:57,410 --> 00:28:58,880
He tells Kuea everything.

429
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:01,240
