437
00:29:27,470 --> 00:29:28,670
Just sit still.

438
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:32,830
What are you so angry about?

439
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:37,810
Hia Yi!

440
00:29:38,630 --> 00:29:39,910
Is he drunk?

441
00:29:52,470 --> 00:29:53,930
Shit.

442
00:29:55,870 --> 00:29:57,470
