446
00:30:06,790 --> 00:30:07,900
Except my time.

447
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:10,120
You should make time for him then.

448
00:30:10,210 --> 00:30:11,450
His time means

449
00:30:11,970 --> 00:30:13,690
he wants me to go back home.

450
00:30:14,190 --> 00:30:15,730
