is that you can keep an eye on my behavior?

559
00:39:45,610 --> 00:39:48,450
Please excuse me if you're just here to pick a fight with me.

560
00:39:49,330 --> 00:39:50,010
Wait.

561
00:39:51,270 --> 00:39:52,170
Let's go on a date.

562
00:39:53,570 --> 00:39:54,310
This evening.

563
00:39:56,130 --> 00:39:56,670
Huh?

564
00:39:57,730 --> 00:39:58,830
A date?

565
00:39:59,190 --> 00:40:00,990
We still have to go on dates?

566
00:40:01,990 --> 00:40:04,990
I thought we no longer had this rule ever since I moved in with you.

567
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:07,510
Nu-Kuea.

568
00:40:08,270 --> 00:40:14,650
The reason I wanted you to move in is not only so that I can always keep an eye on you.

569
00:40:15,370 --> 00:40:18,050
I also want us to know more about each other.

570
00:40:18,490 --> 00:40:20,210
And about this dating thing.

571
00:40:22,910 --> 00:40:25,690
I want to make up for all the dates we've had before.

572
00:40:25,950 --> 00:40:26,850
After this,

573
00:40:28,090 --> 00:40:29,670
I think we shouldn't have a rule

574
00:40:29,850 --> 00:40:31,550
to only go on dates every Friday.

575
00:40:31,790 --> 00:40:33,510
We can go on a date

576
00:40:34,370 --> 00:40:35,910
whenever we want.

577
00:40:36,430 --> 00:40:37,930
Are you okay with that?

578
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:42,750
Yes, Hia.

579
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:47,690
I will pick you up at 5 p.m.

580
00:40:48,490 --> 00:40:49,990
I have to go to work now.

581
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:10,690
Is he possessed by a ghost?

582
00:41:11,930 --> 00:41:13,010
But...

583
00:41:30,220 --> 00:41:31,060
Nu-Kuea.

584
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:33,780
If you don't like anything, just let me know.

585
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:35,460
Don't hesitate.

586
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:37,960
Okay, Hia.

587
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:40,060
But...

588
00:41:40,700 --> 00:41:43,520
I'm still not used to this version of you.

589
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:45,100
Can I ask you something?

590
00:41:45,980 --> 00:41:47,160
What are you thinking?

591
00:41:48,740 --> 00:41:49,820
Like I told you.

592
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:54,820
I think we should get to know each other better.

593
00:41:55,660 --> 00:41:57,320
We should try new things.

594
00:41:57,920 --> 00:41:59,120
Like today.

595
00:42:00,940 --> 00:42:01,760
But today...

596
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:03,900
we've come to the same restaurant.

597
00:42:12,620 --> 00:42:13,420
But,

598
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:14,880
it's fine.

599
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:18,640
It's the same restaurant, but the atmosphere between us has changed.

600
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:21,980
It feels new to me.

601
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:24,520
Wow!

602
00:42:24,980 --> 00:42:29,340
This cauliflower looks so good. Do you want to try it? I'll give it to you.

603
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:31,520
That's a broccoli, Nu-Kuea.

604
00:42:36,140 --> 00:42:37,340
Oh, it really is a broccoli.

605
00:42:37,340 --> 00:42:40,540
I'm not that knowledgeable about food, Hia.

606
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:44,560
It's okay. I understand.

607
00:42:50,720 --> 00:42:51,740
Let me do it for you.

608
00:42:51,740 --> 00:42:53,720
It's okay. I can do it.

609
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:55,960
It's okay, Hia.

610
00:42:56,320 --> 00:42:57,520
Let me pour it for you.

611
00:42:57,520 --> 00:43:00,320
Or else it won't feel like we're on a date.

612
00:43:13,680 --> 00:43:15,640
All dishes have been served.

613
00:43:15,640 --> 00:43:18,180
If you're not satisfied with anything, please let me know.

614
00:43:18,180 --> 00:43:19,020
Okay.

615
00:43:19,380 --> 00:43:22,640
You guys are so cute.

616
00:43:22,880 --> 00:43:26,060
Big brother is taking his little brother out for dinner.

617
00:43:26,320 --> 00:43:27,440
It's very heartwarming to see.

618
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:28,720
This makes me miss my family.

619
00:43:29,020 --> 00:43:31,140
If you need anything else, please let me know.

620
00:43:54,860 --> 00:43:55,740
Nu-Kuea.

621
00:43:59,160 --> 00:44:00,800
You don't have to count today as a date.

622
00:44:02,520 --> 00:44:03,080
Hm?

623
00:44:04,520 --> 00:44:06,280
Just think that I took you out for a normal dinner.

624
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:08,260
I'll take you out on another date.

625
00:44:09,460 --> 00:44:10,980
Let's go somewhere...

626
00:44:11,440 --> 00:44:12,700
we've never been to together before.

627
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:13,940
What do you think?

628
00:44:15,660 --> 00:44:16,840
It's okay, Hia.

629
00:44:18,460 --> 00:44:20,180
I think...

630
00:44:21,060 --> 00:44:24,100
a date is not that important anymore.

631
00:44:25,380 --> 00:44:26,680
Is there something wrong?

632
00:44:30,280 --> 00:44:31,740
I think that...

633
00:44:32,200 --> 00:44:33,340
maybe...

634
00:44:34,160 --> 00:44:36,660
"date" is just another word.

635
00:44:38,460 --> 00:44:39,920
The fact that we're spending time together like this

636
00:44:40,580 --> 00:44:42,160
is even more meaningful than a date.

637
00:44:44,260 --> 00:44:45,240
I don't understand.

638
00:44:46,000 --> 00:44:47,800
The reason you want to call off our engagement

639
00:44:48,100 --> 00:44:50,180
is because I don't pay enough attention to you, isn't it?

640
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:53,360
That's absolutely right.

641
00:44:56,360 --> 00:44:57,860
I'm sorry.

642
00:44:58,260 --> 00:44:59,420
I didn't mean to say that.

643
00:44:59,720 --> 00:45:00,640
It's okay.

644
00:45:00,640 --> 00:45:01,700
I understand.

645
00:45:02,440 --> 00:45:04,180
I'm trying to improve myself.

646
00:45:04,900 --> 00:45:06,100
You're not okay with that?

647
00:45:08,460 --> 00:45:09,960
It's fine.

648
00:45:10,900 --> 00:45:12,440
But I'm just not used to it yet.

649
00:45:12,940 --> 00:45:15,080
You were still teasing me yesterday.

650
00:45:16,320 --> 00:45:18,700
That's because you're always sneaking around.

651
00:45:18,980 --> 00:45:20,680
How can I not keep an eye on you?

652
00:45:21,280 --> 00:45:23,040
You also like to tease me.

653
00:45:23,200 --> 00:45:25,020
You also scold me.

654
00:45:25,620 --> 00:45:27,480
How can I dare to show you my true self?

655
00:45:33,040 --> 00:45:35,260
But...this is who I am.

656
00:45:35,840 --> 00:45:39,640
The more you know me, the more I seem to be naughty, right?

657
00:45:40,780 --> 00:45:42,440
You can be naughty as much as you want.

658
00:45:43,680 --> 00:45:46,440
I just want you to feel comfortable being yourself.

659
00:45:48,940 --> 00:45:50,260
You too.

660
00:45:51,220 --> 00:45:53,800
You don't have to change yourself for me.

661
00:45:54,500 --> 00:45:56,480
You make me so confused already.

662
00:45:58,740 --> 00:46:00,420
I guess we both have to make some adjustments.

663
00:46:01,360 --> 00:46:02,760
If two people love each other,

664
00:46:03,440 --> 00:46:04,860
they should adapt towards one another.

665
00:46:05,800 --> 00:46:07,380
Find comfort in each other.

666
00:46:09,980 --> 00:46:11,040
Um.

667
00:46:13,340 --> 00:46:14,900
I will try.

668
00:46:15,180 --> 00:46:16,620
But if it comes to cooking,

669
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:19,080
I admit that I'm not good at it.

670
00:46:21,380 --> 00:46:23,940
But...I will try to improve myself.

671
00:46:28,260 --> 00:46:30,180
And also...

672
00:46:31,380 --> 00:46:34,220
I haven't said that I wouldn't call off the engagement.

673
00:46:35,140 --> 00:46:37,680
Don't try to fool me with sweet words.

674
00:47:15,280 --> 00:47:16,500
You're awake?

675
00:47:17,460 --> 00:47:18,400
Are you hungry?

676
00:47:21,460 --> 00:47:22,100
Yes.

677
00:47:23,240 --> 00:47:24,420
What are you cooking?

678
00:47:24,540 --> 00:47:25,640
Do you want some help?

679
00:47:28,740 --> 00:47:30,380
You can help me cut the salted eggs.

680
00:47:30,860 --> 00:47:32,060
Just cut it into slices.

681
00:47:32,360 --> 00:47:33,500
I'm going to make spicy salted egg salad.

682
00:47:34,100 --> 00:47:35,280
It's not that complicated.

683
00:47:36,420 --> 00:47:38,100
You can do it, Kuea!

684
00:48:12,020 --> 00:48:13,320
That's dangerous!

685
00:48:16,460 --> 00:48:18,040
If you don't know how to do it, why didn't you just tell me?

686
00:48:18,180 --> 00:48:19,500
You're an adult now.

687
00:48:33,840 --> 00:48:35,380
I can do it.

688
00:48:40,840 --> 00:48:44,040
Who uses such a big knife to slice an egg?

689
00:48:45,480 --> 00:48:46,900
Go sit there and wait.

690
00:48:47,080 --> 00:48:48,160
I'll do it myself.

691
00:49:11,780 --> 00:49:12,900
Nu-Kuea.

692
00:49:17,340 --> 00:49:18,400
Why are you crying?

693
00:49:20,680 --> 00:49:22,960
I can't do anything, right?

694
00:49:24,760 --> 00:49:26,620
Everything I do is wrong.

695
00:49:31,180 --> 00:49:32,440
I didn't mean it like that.

696
00:49:36,160 --> 00:49:37,880
I raised my voice because I was scared.

697
00:49:40,220 --> 00:49:41,900
I was afraid that you'd cut yourself.

698
00:49:45,940 --> 00:49:47,300
I'm not good enough.

699
00:49:48,960 --> 00:49:50,940
I'm just a burden to you.

700
00:49:55,080 --> 00:49:56,080
I understand now.

701
00:49:58,660 --> 00:50:00,660
Why you don't love me.

702
00:53:14,300 --> 00:53:15,060
Whoa!

703
00:53:15,540 --> 00:53:16,500
Is this yours?

704
00:53:16,940 --> 00:53:17,700
Get in.

705
00:53:17,700 --> 00:53:20,420
This is where you think I'd want to come for a date?

706
00:53:20,540 --> 00:53:22,460
This outfit looks good on you.

707
00:53:22,460 --> 00:53:23,900
Hia, you're acting weird.

708
00:53:23,900 --> 00:53:26,020
I like to see you making a fuss. It's funny.

709
00:53:26,020 --> 00:53:27,820
I'll keep teasing you like this for a really long time.

710
00:53:27,820 --> 00:53:29,100
Hia, are you stressed about work?

711
00:53:29,100 --> 00:53:30,580
Or is it because...

712
00:53:30,580 --> 00:53:33,100
Is it because I asked you to come back and stay with me?

713
00:53:33,100 --> 00:53:34,460
You didn't bring Kon-Diao with you?

714
00:53:34,540 --> 00:53:36,860
Is it okay to leave him alone at home?

715
00:53:36,940 --> 00:53:39,500
You never let Nu-Kuea and Kon-Diao come to Pentagon.

716
00:53:39,500 --> 00:53:41,700
You're okay with bringing him here now?

717
00:53:41,700 --> 00:53:42,820
From now on,

718
00:53:42,820 --> 00:53:45,100
there will be no more secrets between Nu-Kuea and me.

719
00:53:45,100 --> 00:53:47,700
If I want him to tell me everything,

720
00:53:48,740 --> 00:53:51,220
I must let him into my world first.
